HEADWORD: Leucopyrite
<hw>Leu*cop"y*rite</hw> <pr>(l⟦usl⟧*k⟦ocr⟧p"⟦icr⟧*r⟦imac⟧t)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Leuco-</ets> + <ets>pyrites</ets>.]</ety>
